songs.title: Clique
songs.lyrics:
My clique is killing competition, everybody getting jealous
My girl is bad as hell and yo girl is fat as Adelle is
Nothing but the truth I got no reason to embellish
Where your bitch at, have you seen her on my wiener call her relish
Everyone's a critic, they just mad because I did it
Adjusting like a snap and they not budging like a fitted
So tell me if you wit it, we could take it to the top
Me and my click is winning we ain't never gonna stop
The blood of an insomniac mix it with some cognac
Repping for my hood like a phoenix on my Pontiac
High definition, I'm trying new positions
Staying on my grind 'cuz in my mind is a vision
Got my pants sagging, slay a dragon with my hands tied
If I run for president I'm winning by a landslide
Built it from the bottom, never got no help
The only person in my click is my goddamn self
